&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Significant functionality enhancements with 31 improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Major stability improvements with 23 bug fixes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Documentation updates with 25 improvements&lt;/li&gt;
